text: Huỳnh Tấn Hùng (born 17 June 1992) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a midfielders for XSKT Cần Thơ. On 4 July 2015 Huỳnh scored in a 4-3 shock win over Đồng Nai in what was only Cần Thơ's second win of the 2015 season. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:XSKT Cần Thơ F.C. players Category:V.League 1 players Category:Association football midfielders
